//     - Port list (clk_i/rst_ni removed, input→right, output→left)
//     - SHA-256/512 bitwise expressions
//     - Basic match/case structure for result mux
//   Manual fixes:
//     - Restored missing AES function call assignments (aes32esi_gen, aes32esmi_gen, etc.)
//     - Restored missing shift-row assignments (sr, sr_inv)
//     - Restored missing 64-bit AES assignments (aes64es_gen, aes64esm_gen, etc.)
//     - Structured conditional blocks: signals gated by ZKN/RVB and IS_XLEN32/IS_XLEN64
//     - Replication operators converted with [MANUAL-CLEANUP-NEEDED] annotations
//     - Concatenation operators {a,b} → #{a, b}
//     - Removed duplicate trailing conditional block comments
